{
  "stem": "150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we saw one guy jump up and down, and yelling and screaming and waving his arms.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was pointing at the tanks, and the tanks had white stars on them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was the Americans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- and then all of a sudden, there were trucks on the road, the American trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Americans were throwing food down from the trucks-- white bread which didn't taste like any white bread I ever had.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was delicious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were giving us little c-rations, little round cans with spam and ham and cheese.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were throwing cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the next thing you knew, a couple of trucks pulled up, and soldiers came out with big sort of pumps with blunt noses, and they pumped DDT into our sleeves and pants and everything to kill the lice.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I saw a couple of Hungarians who had gotten a horse and a wagon, and they were on the horse and a wagon spurring it on, yelling, we're going to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We're going to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know how far they got, but that's where they were going.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was a sort of a celebratory thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were some people got together in a circle were beating up a kapo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The Germans had already been go-- had already gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then all of us were taken to sort of a hospital complex in Landsberg, which became the displaced person camp for that particular bunch of people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And little by little, others started coming from around the countryside from other camps to the point where that hospital complex had, oh, maybe 1,000, 1,500 people in it-- mostly men-- just a few women, and hardly any kids.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
